The drama competition in a very original and raw form. 
Be it socially, politically or artistically motivated, 
get inspired as teams perform and communicate to become 
the drama kings/queens in an exuberant combination of 
drama, music and dialogue.
<br>
<br>
<b>Rules and Regulations</b>
<br>
<br>
Theme- <i>open</i>.
<br>
Time Limit  15 to 25 minutes.
<br>
Number of teams per college 1 max.
<br>
Event Fees  500/- for the complete group.
<br>
Bring your own costumes and props.
<br>
The act should be either in English or Hindi.
